entirely in CSS, no React code changes are needed to restyle the components."},"639":{"id":"/docs/customize/theming-15","page_id":"/docs/customize/theming","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/customize/theming#overview","content":"Offers multiple prebuilt themes like luxury, retro, arctic etc. These themes are highly customizable, allowing individual tokens to be tweaked or entirely new color palettes to be created to match specific brand aesthetics."},"640":{"id":"/docs/customize/theming-16","page_id":"/docs/customize/theming","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/customize/theming#overview","content":"Use the theme variables (like `--color-primary` and `--shadow-md`) via standard Tailwind utilities (for example, `bg-primary`, `text-primary`, `shadow-md`)."},"641":{"id":"/docs/customize/theming-17","page_id":"/docs/customize/theming","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/customize/theming#overview","content":"Override any theme variables globally by redefining them in an `@theme { ... }` block after importing the CSS."},"642":{"id":"/docs/customize/theming-18","page_id":"/docs/customize/theming","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/customize/theming#overview","content":"Reboot provides a base CSS reset with element-specific styles for consistent design across browsers."},"643":{"id":"/docs/customize/theming-19","page_id":"/docs/customize/theming","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/customize/theming#available-themes","content":"Here is a quick overview of the available prebuilt themes:"},"644":{"id":"/docs/customize/theming-20","page_id":"/docs/customize/theming","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/customize/theming#available-themes","content":"The signature Hummingbird theme with balanced neutrals and vibrant blue\naccents."},"645":{"id":"/docs/customize/theming-21","page_id":"/docs/customize/theming","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/customize/theming#available-themes","content":"Rich maroon and golden tones crafted for a refined, premium appearance."},"646":