nd `Table.Caption`\nrender their native table elements and accept only `className` alongside their\nstandard element props."],[473,"`Tabs.List` uses the bordered style by default. Set `defaultValue` to select the initial tab."],[537,"`text-muted`"],[523,"`text-primary`"],[518,"`text-red-500`"],[567,"1\\. Custom dark mode selector"],[905,"1\\. Install Tailwind CSS"],[906,"2\\. Install Hummingbird React"],[568,"2\\. Set the initial theme"],[569,"3\\. Add a theme toggle"],[907,"3\\. Import CSS"],[908,"4\\. Use components"],[607,"A \"Reboot\" stylesheet (like Hummingbird's Reboot) resets browser styles and sets up a foundation for consistent design. Using CSS variables in Reboot makes it easy to customize base styles without editing the core CSS — just override the variables."],[779,"A `Button` can be placed alongside the form control as a trailing action."],[880,"A `Col` without any props creates equal-width columns for every screen size."],[301,"A `ListGroup` renders a vertical list of `ListGroup.Item` elements."],[237,"A draggable, dismissible panel that slides in from any edge of the screen."],[289,"A flexible container for displaying a series of related content as a vertical list."],[141,"A flexible content container with header, body, and footer regions."],[396,"A floating panel anchored to a trigger, built on Radix Popover with Hummingbird's popover styling."],[727,"A label that floats above the control once it is focused or filled."],[225,"A layer that covers the inert portion of the view when the dialog is open. `Dialog.Content` renders this part automatically; use its `overlayProps` prop to customize it."],[589,"A list of theme variables that are overridden when dark mode is active."],[196,"A modal dialog built on Radix UI that traps focus, locks scroll, and dismisses on backdrop click or Escape."],[333,"A responsive navigation header with a brand, links, text, and a collapsible menu."],[461,"A set of layered panels whose triggers switch which panel is shown."],[68,"A small count or status descriptor for UI elements."],[487,"A small label that appears on hover or keyboard focus to describe the element beneath the pointer."],[709,"A styled native checkbox, including the indeterminate state."],[786,"A styled native radio button, with an optional group wrapper."],[804,"A styled native range slider for selecting a value from a range."],[818,"A styled native select for choosing one option from a list."],[311,"A styled navigation list of links with active and disabled states."],[425,"A styled table for displaying rows of data."],[836,"A toggle switch built on a native checkbox with role=\"switch\"."],[254,"A toggleable menu of actions or links, anchored to a trigger and positioned by Radix UI."],[2,"A vertically stacked set of interactive headings that each reveal a section of content."],[763,"Accepts the same `variant`, `size`, `color`, `state`, and `className` props as `FormControl`."],[1,"Accordion"],[7,"Accordion"],[11,"Accordion.Content"],[9,"Accordion.Header"],[8,"Accordion.Item"],[10,"Accordion.Trigger"],[292,"Actionable"],[532,"Actions colors (generate all color-related utilities)"],[316,"Active"],[434,"Active"],[291,"Active and disabled"],[477,"Add `disabled` to a `Tabs.Trigger` to prevent its panel from being selected."],[15,"Add `disabled` to an `Accordion.Item` to prevent it from opening, or to the\n`Accordion` root to disable every item."],[601,"Address"],[25,"Alert"],[32,"Alert"],[858,"All breakpoints"],[553,"All components accept a `className` prop. Custom classes are merged with the component classes, so any Tailwind utility can be applied on top. For example, rounded pill buttons can be created by adding the `rounded-full` class."],[918,"All components accept a `className` prop. Custom classes are merged with the component classes, so Tailwind utility classes can be used to adjust any component."],[576,"All components rely on the same semantic tokens:"],[686,"All Tailwind utility classes can be applied to Hummingbird React components through the `className` prop. Custom classes are merged with the component classes, so utilities can adjust spacing, typography, radius, and more without writing custom CSS. This page lists the most frequently used utilities; see the official Tailwind CSS docs for the complete reference."],[610,"All the headings (`h1` to `h6`) in Hummingbird are styled with CSS variables for font size, weight, line height, and margin."],[337,"Always collapsed"],[228,"An accessible title to be announced when the dialog is opened. Renders an `h6` element by default."],[54,"An avatar renders an image with a fallback for when the image is unavailable."],[62,"An element that renders when the image hasn't loaded. This means whilst it's loading, or if there was an error."],[161,"An icon-only button for dismissing content."],[42,"An image element with a text fallback for representing a user or entity."],[176,"An interactive component that expands and collapses a single panel of content."],[229,"An optional accessible description to be announced when the dialog is opened."],[416,"An optional element to position the `Popover.Content` against. If this part is not used, the content will position alongside the `Popover.Trigger`."],[6,"API Reference"],[31,"API Reference"],[48,"API Reference"],[75,"API Reference"],[91,"API Reference"],[108,"API Reference"],[129,"API Reference"],[148,"API Reference"],[166,"API Reference"],[181,"API Reference"],[203,"API Reference"],[242,"API Reference"],[260,"API Reference"],[296,"API Reference"],[318,"API Reference"],[341,"API Reference"],[377,"API Reference"],[401,"API Reference"],[439,"API Reference"],[467,"API Reference"],[492,"API Reference"],[716,"API Reference"],[731,"API Reference"],[751,"API Reference"],[774,"API Reference"],[792,"API Reference"],[809,"API Reference"],[825,"API Reference"],[842,"API Reference"],[873,"API Reference"],[854,"Auto-layout columns"],[626,"Available themes"],[41,"Avatar"],[49,"Avatar"],[51,"Avatar.Fallbac